{"tid":2151270,"cid":15,"subCid":0,"title":"【摸魚手札】肥佬黎，呢鋪我撐你-渾水","createTime":"2020-08-11T10:01:56.000Z","updateTime":"2020-08-11T10:01:56.000Z","uid":25558,"like":2,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":1,"replies":[{"pid":"234099bf478ad45df3eced813f3768b072d78955","tid":2151270,"uid":25558,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-11T10:01:56.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/finance/20200811/WHS7WYUVXFBMZD2C5S67UXVV2U/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Ffinance%2F20200811%2FWHS7WYUVXFBMZD2C5S67UXVV2U%2F&d=9ox5Qr7lvCKhSYdyRcf9FvjlBAU1VhUdv3lOLHlSYeE%3D&h=40b8177a\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Ffinance%2F20200811%2FWHS7WYUVXFBMZD2C5S67UXVV2U%2F&h=391327b1\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.appledaily.com/finance/20200811/WHS7WYUVXFBMZD2C5S67UXVV2U/</a><br />\n<br />\n節錄<br />\n<br />\n【摸魚手札】肥佬黎，呢鋪我撐你-渾水<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/resizer/qrny61H8Wj7uln8NYZW0Wj6kv90=/1280x853/filters:quality(100)/cloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com/appledaily/H6L57BKTQ5AEXDVCHQTKZR7HWE.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fresizer%2Fqrny61H8Wj7uln8NYZW0Wj6kv90%3D%2F1280x853%2Ffilters%3Aquality%28100%29%2Fcloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com%2Fappledaily%2FH6L57BKTQ5AEXDVCHQTKZR7HWE.jpg&h=7b8f1564&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n■警方高調入《蘋果》掃場，壹傳媒居然沒有停牌。 資料圖片<br />\n<br />\n肥佬黎被國安捉走了，。。。。。。。。。。<br />\n<br />\n出奇地，這樣高調掃場，公司居然沒有停牌。<br />\n<br />\n早排蘋果出現專欄作家大退潮，我自薦不收錢寫多一日。壹傳媒的國際線由我提出，芳鄰馮睎乾力推，能夠做的我都做了。萬念俱灰下，剛好博客無神論者巴別塔說他要放下對壹的成見，買入股票支持，然後我也不理性地跟着他買入，也出了disclaimer說這是不理性，停牌就是當刻最大的風險。買壹傳媒對公司有好處，員工有股份，如果股價升，也是實現對良心媒體人的支持。<br />\n<br />\n後來立場偏黃的公司都有異動，連帶本地傳媒股也逆市升，到底是炒黃色資金，炒被中共買盤還是炒家momentum trading？這我就不知了。我非常清楚這贏回來的錢不能花掉，私下我有一個獎學金，派給上年受了苦的中大師弟妹，本來我只贏了7萬多，今次我決定加到10萬回饋同學。這事不知怎樣上了西方媒體，我也被低級打手抹黑。<br />\n<br />\n我忠於我自己，德不孤，必有鄰。<br />\n<br />\n渾水<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"http://fb.com/muddydirtywater\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Ffb.com%2Fmuddydirtywater&d=9ox5Qr7lvCKhSYdyRcf9FvjlBAU1VhUdv3lOLHlSYeE%3D&h=a930b827\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">fb.com/muddydirtywater</a>"}]}